     2| * Conway Inference Client
     3| *
     4| * Wraps Conway's /v1/chat/completions endpoint (OpenAI-compatible).
     5| * The automaton pays for its own thinking through Conway credits.
     6| */
     7|
     8|import type {
     9|  InferenceClient,
